				</tr>
				<tr>
					<td><p>Un ou plusieurs noms de police, notamment les noms g&eacute;n&eacute;riques suivants: <span class="literal">serif</span> | <span class="literal">sans-serif</span> | <span class="literal">cursive</span> | <span class="literal">fantasy</span> | <span class="literal">monospace</span>.</p>
					</td>
				</tr>
